Book two of the stormlight archives
Follows a dude named Kaladin who saved this dude named Dalinar's life and went from being worse than a slave to being in charge of 1000 troops.  He knows how to fight.
Also follows a dude named Dalinar who figures out he's not crazy but is seeing visions when it rains.  He almost gets assassinated but then becomes stronger because of it.
Also follows a chick named Shallan to is good at drawing and making people more than what they seem.  She learns how perception is reality and how to bend perception.